window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Four unforgettable full-length romance novels from NYT and USA Today Bestselling Author A.L. Jackson</i></b></p> <p>They all ended up in the small town of Redemption Hills to put the dangers of their previous lives behind.<br> But they had no idea they would all find the women who show them their pasts don't dictate their future.</p> <p><b>Give Me a Reason</b><br> A single-dad, enemies-to-lovers stand-alone romance about a jaded club owner and his son’s teacher...</p> <p><b>Say It's Forever</b><br> A close proximity, single-mom stand-alone romance about a woman on the run and the man who will do anything to save her...</p> <p><b>Never Look Back</b><br> An enemies-to-lovers, second-chance stand-alone romance about conquering the past that swore to keep them apart...</p> <p><b>Promise Me Always</b><br> A single dad, fake fiancée romance about a grumpy mountain man and the woman who gives him a chance at the life he never thought he deserved...</p>"; 
